    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Accesing text file using Shell Script.]]></title>
    <link href="http://kapoorabhish.github.io/blog/2013/06/14/accesing-csv-file-using-shell-script/"/>
    <updated>2013-06-14T08:19:00+05:30</updated>
